room_title: Escape room "Apartment 460" by Locked 460 Escape Rooms in Grand Rapids
room_description: It’s 1983. You’ve seen and heard strange things coming from the apartment across the hall these last few months. You recruit some friends, wait until your neighbor leaves, and decide to investigate. But when you break in, you have tripped a silent alarm. He knows you are there and is coming back to protect his creepy secrets. Gather the evidence you need and get out before he returns.
